        {
            "title": "韓國KOSPI因晶片股重挫觸發熔斷機制，交易一度暫停",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/K9VfFA5C.E8ck1rYKJ6CSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED220BB_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週四早盤，韓國綜合股價指數（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"KOSPI\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:KOSPI;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/KOSPI\">KOSPI</a>）因本地晶片製造股遭受重創，開盤即急劇下滑，全球科技股拋售潮重壓相關板塊，觸發熔斷機制，交易被迫暫停。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">KOSPI開盤後不久暴跌逾6%，跌至7,769.16點，觸發賣方熔斷機制，交易暫停五分鐘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四的交易暫停，是KOSPI今年以來因市場劇烈波動而多次觸發熔斷的最新一例，根源在於重量級晶片股的大幅震盪所引發的高度不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三星電子（KS:005930）與SK海力士（KS:000660）是此次波動的核心。這兩家記憶體晶片巨頭今年因人工智慧（AI）需求大幅攀升而股價強勁上漲，在KOSPI中的市值佔比舉足輕重，並在近幾個月內多次引發指數盤中劇烈震盪。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e9a8f803-bd7f-39a4-9b92-42ee8d14a72a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每當AI領域出現負面消息，這兩隻股票便會急速回落，進而拖累整體KOSPI走低。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四，三星電子下跌7.3%，SK海力士則重挫近9%。導火索來自《The Information》的一篇報導，指OpenAI已開發出軟體優化技術，可將AI模型的推理運算需求削減一半——這意味著未來運行AI模型所需的處理器數量可能大幅減少。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，有報導稱Meta Platforms計劃出售多餘的雲端運算容量，這一趨勢暗示企業或將更充分地挖掘現有硬體的潛力，而非採購更新、更昂貴的晶片，進一步加劇了市場對AI晶片需求下滑的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對記憶體晶片製造商而言，壓力更是雪上加霜——有報導顯示，蘋果公司正與被列入黑名單的中國記憶體晶片廠商洽談採購事宜，原因是高記憶體價格帶來的成本壓力日益沉重。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多重負面因素的疊加，對晶片及AI相關股票造成沉重打擊。這些股票原本是推動KOSPI今年強勁上漲的核心動力，但隨著市場對AI與晶片股能否持續上行的疑慮不斷升溫，近幾週漲勢已明顯放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，KOSPI在2026年迄今仍累計上漲近83%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8Bkospi%E5%9B%A0%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%82%A1%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E7%86%94%E6%96%B7%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E5%BA%A6%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C-055951434.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 14:06:58",
