        {
            "title": "蘋果計劃在2027年初前推出至少5款新iPhone機型，日經報道",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zW5WwSbUa.87sSem6VxgqA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEE1K1DD_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 據日經亞洲週四報道，蘋果公司（Apple）正積極擴充其iPhone產品線，計劃在2027年前推出多款新機型，並已上調首款可折疊iPhone的生產目標，以期在高端智慧型手機市場進一步鞏固其地位，儘管目前供應鏈壓力持續加大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日經亞洲引述知情人士消息稱，蘋果計劃在2026年下半年至2027年上半年期間，推出至少五款全新iPhone機型，是近年來產品發布週期中規模最為龐大的一次。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-52588fb2-34c0-3d9e-8bb9-08d87ccef97b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道指出，蘋果已要求供應商為今年生產約1,000萬部可折疊iPhone做好準備，較早前預測的700萬至800萬部有所上調。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉正值各大智慧型手機廠商競相擴大可折疊產品陣容之際，目前該市場由三星電子（KS:005930）及華為技術等中國廠商主導。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果近期已上調多款Mac及iPad機型的售價，理由是記憶體及儲存晶片成本上漲；公司管理層亦警告，若零組件費用持續攀升，未來iPhone的定價或將受到影響。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%9C%A82027%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E5%89%8D%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%915%E6%AC%BE%E6%96%B0iphone%E6%A9%9F%E5%9E%8B-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%93%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93-044501939.html",
